    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员绕过国会向阿联酋、科威特和约旦出售武器</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/wartime-emergency-congress-weapons.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[其中一些价值超过 230 亿美元的拟议销售正在接受审查，而另一些则从未提交给国会。政府正在未经国会批准的情况下推动这些计划的通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/us/politics/wartime-emergency-congress-weapons.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 20:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
